<subSubSection pageId="241" pageNumber="846" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="241.[2061,2664,2424,2851]" lastBlockId="241.[1446,2652,2856,3480]" pageId="241" pageNumber="846">
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Thomas" baseAuthorityYear="1888" box="[2063,2242,2503,2537]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Rattus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="241" pageNumber="846" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="praetor">Rattus praetor</taxonomicName>
is included in a clade of Re- cent New Guinea native species and seems to be close to 
<taxonomicName box="[2253,2355,2582,2616]" genus="Rat" pageId="241" pageNumber="846" rank="species" species="steini">R. steini</taxonomicName>
(which makesit paraphyletic), 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Thomas" baseAuthorityYear="1904" box="[2199,2328,2621,2655]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Rattus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="241" pageNumber="846" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="mordax">R. mordax</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Taylor &amp; Calaby" authorityYear="1982" box="[2405,2607,2621,2655]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Rattus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="241" pageNumber="846" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="novaeguineae">R. novaeguineae</taxonomicName>
. As currently defined, 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Thomas" baseAuthorityYear="1888" box="[2315,2437,2665,2694]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Rattus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="241" pageNumber="846" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="praetor">R. praetor</taxonomicName>
almost certainly represents multiple species, particularly because there are regularly caught specimens outside the current known distribution that are fairly similar to 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Thomas" baseAuthorityYear="1888" box="[2338,2447,2817,2851]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Rattus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="241" pageNumber="846" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="praetor">R.praetor</taxonomicName>
. The newly described species 
<taxonomicName box="[1656,1777,2856,2890]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Rattus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="241" pageNumber="846" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="nikenii">R. nikenii</taxonomicName>
was previously included in 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Thomas" baseAuthorityYear="1888" box="[2143,2263,2856,2890]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Rattus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="241" pageNumber="846" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="praetor">R. praetor</taxonomicName>
. Two subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
